text_raw:
2. The 31st day of December 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
Domestic, Sexual and Gender-Based Violence Agency Act 2023 (No. 31 of 
2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

20 December, 2023. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 22nd December, 2023.
